message: To get 80 points, combine any 'soft natural' item with any 'soft artificial' item (this gives 30 points). Then, use the 'scissors' tool on that 30-point combined item. Avoid using 'scissors' on 'hard' items as it usually decreases value. The 'frame' tool often yields 20 points for hard items.
